<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Dashy Solar Monitoring System</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f7f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      header {
        background-color: #2c3e50;
        color: white;
        padding: 1em;
        text-align: center;
      }
      nav {
        background-color: #34495e;
        padding: 0.5em;
        text-align: center;
      }
      nav a {
        color: white;
        margin: 0 1em;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      main {
        padding: 2em;
      }
      .selection {
        margin-bottom: 2em;
      }
      .selection label {
        margin-right: 1em;
      }
      .section {
        margin-bottom: 2em;
      }
      footer {
        background-color: #2c3e50;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 1em;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Solar Monitoring System</h1>
      <p>Real-time Energy Tracking for Home and Commercial Use</p>
    </header>
    <nav>
      <a href="#overview">Overview</a>
      <a href="#inverters">Inverters</a>
      <a href="#sense">Sense Monitor</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <main>
      <section id="overview" class="section">
        <h2>Choose Your Application</h2>
        <div class="selection">
          <label>
            <input type="radio" name="usage" value="home" checked /> Home Use
          </label>
          <label>
            <input type="radio" name="usage" value="commercial" /> Commercial
            Use
          </label>
        </div>
        <p>
          Select your application to customize the solar monitoring system to
          your needs. Whether for residential or commercial purposes, our system
          adapts to provide optimal performance and insights.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section id="inverters" class="section">
        <h2>Integrated Inverters</h2>
        <p>
          Our system includes high-efficiency inverters that convert solar
          energy into usable electricity. These inverters are compatible with
          both home and commercial setups, ensuring seamless energy conversion
          and monitoring.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section id="sense" class="section">
        <h2>Sense Energy Monitor Integration</h2>
        <p>
          We've integrated the
          <a href="https://sense.app/" target="_blank">Sense Energy Monitor</a>
          into our system to provide real-time insights into your energy
          consumption and solar production. Monitor your energy usage, identify
          trends, and optimize your energy efficiency with ease.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section id="contact" class="section">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          For more information or to get started with your solar monitoring
          system, please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:info@solarmonitoring.com">info@solarmonitoring.com</a
          >.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer>&copy; 2025 Solar Monitoring System. All rights reserved.</footer>
  </body>
</html>
